item.title: How do i download a auto please help
item.dc:creator: @Bebemycat2 Bebe
item.description:
@Bebemycat2 wrote:

Download and install SCAR from http://freddy1990.com/scar.php
Then follow this tutorial to download SRL: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,263470.0.html

You can find scripts to run in SCAR on these forums at http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php#2 or in the “SRL portal”. I would highly recommend SRL scripts as they are usally the most advanced and up to date.
